WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.543
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:01.543 --> 00:00:03.720
I'm excited to be with you all today.

00:00:03.720 --> 00:00:05.094
I have a word for you.

00:00:05.803 --> 00:00:11.085
I want to go back to the things the Lord has told you before.

00:00:11.085 --> 00:00:20.939
Regarding the 24th—I was interceding for this day for a long time before I told you all about it.

00:00:20.939 --> 00:00:33.696
I mentioned it a week or two ago, that the 24th was a significant day and that the Lord was warning me in prayer to pray over that day.

00:00:34.074 --> 00:00:41.709
I am trying to tell you all, I've known about this for quite a while, so I've been praying over the 24th.

00:00:42.223 --> 00:00:48.105
The Lord told me it would be part of the first domino.

00:00:48.105 --> 00:00:57.344
When the 24th came, He told me, "You'll see the first domino start to fall for the Antichrist system.

00:00:57.344 --> 00:01:01.540
" The new system is going to start to manifest.

00:01:01.940 --> 00:01:06.389
But that's whenever He told me, "Who will stand in the gap for America?

00:01:06.389 --> 00:01:08.640
Who will intercede for America?

00:01:09.008 --> 00:01:11.580
" I told you all about that word.

00:01:11.580 --> 00:01:21.959
I didn't really know what was going to happen on the 24th; all I knew is it was significant, and I kept praying over it.

00:01:22.259 --> 00:01:27.280
The closer it got, it felt very heavy in the spirit realm.

00:01:28.947 --> 00:01:35.592
The night before, I was up almost all night praying on the 23rd, interceding and standing in the gap for what was coming.

00:01:37.755 --> 00:01:39.554
The closer it got, the heavier it started to feel.

00:01:50.807 --> 00:01:57.959
I trust the spirits to make sure it wasn't forebodings, but then I felt such an urgency.

00:01:57.959 --> 00:02:05.423
When it hit about six in the morning my time, it started as an urgency.

00:02:05.423 --> 00:02:09.920
I felt like I was being pushed in that river.

00:02:10.785 --> 00:02:20.819
The intercessory prayer was so intense for what was going on in the spirit realm; it felt like I was being pushed, like, "Hurry, hurry, hurry.

00:02:26.495 --> 00:02:40.965
" As you all know, the BRICS nations came out and announced that Saudi Arabia—the one I told you all about, where the Prince of Saudi Arabia said he would put his boot down on America and join up with others—would join.

00:02:40.965 --> 00:02:45.495
Argentina—I didn't think was going to happen as soon.

00:02:45.495 --> 00:02:53.670
When I was looking in the spirit realm and the Lord was showing me the nations, I told you the Chinese flag went over.

00:02:53.670 --> 00:03:00.140
I thought it was going to be later on how that all happened, whenever it went over Africa and touched down.

00:03:00.140 --> 00:03:07.499
Argentina was invited yesterday, so I was just like, "Wow, this is being sped up big time.

00:03:08.850 --> 00:03:13.508
" I hope you all realize how fast everything is coming at us.

00:03:14.273 --> 00:03:16.180
Jesus Christ is coming.

00:03:17.934 --> 00:03:19.572
I never want to quote a timeframe.

00:03:22.319 --> 00:03:27.560
Everybody asks me in the comment section if I believe it's this year, 2023, 2024, or later.

00:03:28.840 --> 00:03:36.823
I want to keep an urgency so that everyone is looking for Him today.

00:03:38.307 --> 00:03:45.048
I don't want to ever say, "I believe it to be in 2032 or 2030.

00:03:49.689 --> 00:03:59.820
" All we need to do is focus on the fact that Jesus is coming and have an urgency to tell the people around us.

00:04:01.500 --> 00:04:06.840
No matter if it's five years from now, we need to live like it's today.

00:04:06.840 --> 00:04:17.272
Don't live like it's five years from now because a lot of people get a lackadaisical attitude and think if it's five years from now, they're just going to party.

00:04:19.139 --> 00:04:31.139
If you don't have that sense of urgency inside of you, it causes you to be stirred up to witness and live a righteous and holy life.

00:04:34.238 --> 00:04:35.648
Keep your lamp full.

00:04:38.468 --> 00:04:39.680
Occupy until He comes.

00:04:39.680 --> 00:04:48.540
I try not to think about five or ten years; I just act like Jesus is coming right now.

00:04:48.540 --> 00:04:54.233
It could happen right now while I'm talking to you because no man knows the day or the hour.

00:04:55.680 --> 00:05:06.969
I told you all about the aliens and everyone's like, "It must be when Jesus was telling me about the aliens and demonic beings.

00:05:07.406 --> 00:05:10.560
" There's no such thing as aliens; they are demonic spirits.

00:05:17.865 --> 00:05:25.423
What's about to happen is—we're talking about it and seeing it in the news, but this is just the beginning.

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:29.604
Wait until you start seeing the manifestations.

00:05:30.048 --> 00:05:40.089
I really believe there is actually going to be alien demonic stuff on TV, and they're actually going to interview them.

00:05:41.160 --> 00:05:43.027
It's going to be a big deal.

00:05:43.027 --> 00:05:46.080
You're going to see a great deception before long.

00:05:46.080 --> 00:05:52.360
It's not just about things flying around the sky; you're going to start to see some really demonic stuff.

00:05:52.800 --> 00:06:01.680
They're going to try to deceive people into believing there is a people in another universe.

00:06:04.590 --> 00:06:05.873
It's all demonic.

00:06:07.379 --> 00:06:08.559
They're coming to deceive you.

00:06:08.773 --> 00:06:14.670
I know many people will fall for this and start believing we've got to be their friends.

00:06:20.069 --> 00:06:21.344
No, they are demonic spirits.

00:06:23.640 --> 00:06:27.337
Don't be deceived about what's coming in the near future.

00:06:29.137 --> 00:06:39.805
When Jesus took me through the Tribulation with Him, He said one of the major signs before I come back will be major talk about aliens on television.

00:06:42.900 --> 00:06:43.767
This was back in 2014, going on ten years ago.

00:06:43.767 --> 00:06:50.580
When He told me this, I thought it was going to happen right then, but it has been ten years.

00:06:50.580 --> 00:06:53.490
July 6th, 2024, will be ten years.

00:06:53.685 --> 00:06:58.259
I believe we're right there at the door for a major deception on the news.

00:06:58.259 --> 00:07:08.615
Saudi Arabia is going to join the BRICS nations on January 1st, 2024, from what I've understood and the articles I've read.

00:07:08.615 --> 00:07:17.791
That means we have five months left before they jump ship with Argentina, Egypt, and the UAE.

00:07:17.791 --> 00:07:21.486
Eighty percent of the world's oil wealth is joining that.

00:07:25.199 --> 00:07:25.589
This is a huge deal.

00:07:25.589 --> 00:07:29.863
This is the warning I tried to tell you.

00:07:29.863 --> 00:07:36.180
I'm not preaching fear, but there is a great storm coming.

00:07:36.180 --> 00:07:46.259
When I told you about the 24th, it was right then Japan started dumping water from Fukushima.

00:07:46.259 --> 00:07:52.586
They're releasing that toxic water into the Pacific Ocean.

00:07:52.586 --> 00:08:02.427
China then banned the export of seafood from Japan because they are poisoning the ocean with radioactive material.

00:08:02.780 --> 00:08:05.760
This is another huge thing that happened yesterday.

00:08:19.868 --> 00:08:20.220
Then on the 24th, we had President Trump's mugshot.

00:08:20.220 --> 00:08:23.271
That's a big deal.

00:08:25.887 --> 00:08:27.969
It's never happened to a former president.

00:08:27.969 --> 00:08:33.338
This all happened in one day, on the 24th.

00:08:36.120 --> 00:08:43.809
The Lord said the 24th of August will be the beginning; the dominoes will start to fall after that.

00:09:01.569 --> 00:09:01.783
A major event will take place concerning the earthquake.

00:09:01.783 --> 00:09:05.567
I believe we're about to see that major New Madrid fault.

00:09:05.567 --> 00:09:20.843
When I saw the python coming out of the water and wrapping around America and squeezing tight, I believe that's one of the major events we're about to see take place next.

00:09:20.843 --> 00:09:36.849
Then I believe we're about to see a new Democratic candidate, someone who is a superstar concerning their agenda, wanting to take his place because he is not sound.

00:09:36.849 --> 00:09:40.238
I believe we're going to see that soon.

00:09:42.728 --> 00:09:46.046
I could be wrong, but that's just my opinion.

00:09:46.046 --> 00:09:54.690
Whenever I'm praying in the spirit about it, I have an urgency.

00:09:54.690 --> 00:10:00.013
I've seen a short brown-haired woman doing something in November.

00:10:00.013 --> 00:10:11.880
I've seen this, and so I've been praying about that and coming along beside Kamala Harris, kind of like how Ford and Nixon did.

00:10:14.850 --> 00:10:16.333
I believe that's right, and how he ran it until the election.

00:10:36.855 --> 00:10:37.200
I believe I have to be so careful.

00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:49.302
We will see some change take place in the fall.

00:10:49.302 --> 00:10:53.265
There's going to be some changing taking place; there's going to be a shifting, more shifting.

00:10:53.894 --> 00:10:54.839
I've seen it.

00:10:54.839 --> 00:11:05.850
I'm telling you all about the crash of the economy, the crash of the money, and now people go, 'Well, I thought you said it was going to be a financial blessing for the body of Christ.

00:11:05.850 --> 00:11:16.283
' Yes, if you are listening—and this is where I want to tell you—you will not participate in the financial blessing if you're not hearing the Holy Ghost.

00:11:16.283 --> 00:11:20.659
It's not going to happen just by sitting idle.

00:11:20.659 --> 00:11:29.340
You need to be activated, actively praying in the spirit, or praying and asking the Lord, 'Hey Lord, I thank you, Lord.

00:11:29.340 --> 00:11:35.304
' Seed faith—that's another thing you all need to know: every seed produces after its own kind.

00:11:35.304 --> 00:11:38.080
You have to sow to be able to reap.

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:46.440
If you are not a tither, if you're not a giver, if you're not actively sowing, the Lord is going to tell you creative ideas to get wealth.

00:11:46.440 --> 00:11:49.529
You're fooling yourself because he can't trust you.

00:11:49.529 --> 00:11:53.580
If he can't trust you with little, he's not going to make you ruler over much.

00:11:53.580 --> 00:11:58.290
You have to be trusted with the little thing before he gives you the much thing.

00:11:58.605 --> 00:12:07.691
If you can't be trusted in the money thing, and if you would get any kind of wealth, would it destroy you?

00:12:07.691 --> 00:12:22.718
Because he's not going to allow a lot of money to go into your hands to be able to help this end-time harvest—this push for the end-time harvest—if you are not able to be trusted with finances, because he's not going to let you go to hell for money.

00:12:22.718 --> 00:12:27.736
He cares about your soul, so you have to be able to be trusted with what's going to happen.

00:12:27.736 --> 00:12:36.463
So this is where I'm at with it: if you can't believe for five dollars, how can you believe for 500,000 to pay off a church?

00:12:36.463 --> 00:12:37.560
That's what I'm saying.

00:12:37.560 --> 00:12:39.459
You've got to start somewhere.

00:12:39.459 --> 00:12:42.460
Start believing for five dollars for whatever.

00:12:42.460 --> 00:12:46.534
Start believing for a hundred dollars or whatever you're believing for.

00:12:46.534 --> 00:12:48.025
Sow the seed.

00:12:48.025 --> 00:12:51.332
Ten percent of what you earn is what I do.

00:12:51.332 --> 00:12:51.911
I tithe.

00:12:52.500 --> 00:13:00.090
I've been tithing because, bottom line, Pastor Mark, where I worked there at the church, he forced us to tithe.

00:13:00.090 --> 00:13:02.494
If you didn't tithe, they fired you.

00:13:02.494 --> 00:13:08.039
So I've been tithing ever since I started working at the church back in 2003.

00:13:08.039 --> 00:13:12.220
They forced us to tithe and they said, 'If you don't tithe, you're fired.

00:13:12.220 --> 00:13:15.359
' And so I was like, you know, that was a long time ago.

00:13:15.359 --> 00:13:18.480
I mean, that's going on over 20 some years now.

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:24.951
I've been tithing faithfully and giving my 10% and my offerings, believing God for increase.

00:13:24.951 --> 00:13:28.380
And so that's the way we did it.

00:13:28.380 --> 00:13:33.240
We believe by faith for everything we have, whether it's five dollars, ten dollars, whatever.

00:13:33.240 --> 00:13:37.160
You've got to believe God and start saying, 'Lord...

00:13:37.160 --> 00:13:42.180
' And you know, a lot of times you think, 'Well, how's it going to happen?

00:13:42.180 --> 00:13:47.091
How is God going to bring the increase in my house?

00:13:47.091 --> 00:13:50.473
' I don't limit myself to a job.

00:13:50.473 --> 00:13:53.714
I start, 'God, give me an idea.

00:13:53.714 --> 00:13:57.240
' Lord, I'm always thinking outside of the box.

00:13:57.240 --> 00:14:02.169
What can I do to work for myself to create wealth?

00:14:02.169 --> 00:14:04.819
That's when I started doing my dogs.

00:14:11.060 --> 00:14:23.752
I started having these little puppies, and the Lord gave us an idea to help with therapy dogs for people because my little girl is overcoming autism and she loves her little puppy, and my other little daughter loves her puppy.

00:14:35.280 --> 00:14:36.926
So we have these puppies and I sell therapy dogs to special needs kids and to elderly people who need a companion, so there's a lot of people that need these dogs.

00:14:40.249 --> 00:14:43.313
So God gave me the idea for my family because I didn't have a lot of education.

00:14:43.313 --> 00:14:51.866
Of course, you all have heard my testimony about doing something other than cleaning, because I started doing the detailing business.

00:14:53.813 --> 00:14:54.099
I was like, 'Lord...

00:14:54.099 --> 00:15:03.353
' So the Lord gave me an idea, so I started cleaning cars because I used to clean cars for a major ministry.

00:15:08.430 --> 00:15:15.735
I started telling everybody I had an idea of doing mobile detailing, so I got me a mobile detailing trailer and I just go around cleaning cars for people.

00:15:15.735 --> 00:15:21.100
I'd be so excited because I could make a hundred dollars and clean a car.

00:15:23.059 --> 00:15:23.699
I detail, I wax it, do everything.

00:15:24.239 --> 00:15:29.015
I spent several hours doing it, but I got me a helper, and they helped me, and my brother.

00:15:39.986 --> 00:15:40.280
And so we cleaned the cars together and we would do things, wax the cars, and clean the carpets.

00:15:51.319 --> 00:15:51.526
I got me a carpet shampooer.

00:16:01.919 --> 00:16:02.159
I just started asking God for ways to create wealth so that I didn't have to work for seven dollars an hour because I didn't have an education.

00:16:02.159 --> 00:16:05.682
I was like, 'Man, I'm making minimum wage.

00:16:10.905 --> 00:16:11.198
You can't live on minimum wage.

00:16:11.198 --> 00:16:19.680
' And so I cleaned for the church, and they gave me a little raise, but I was still struggling.

00:16:19.680 --> 00:16:23.730
But I would work when I got off of work.

00:16:23.730 --> 00:16:35.580
After working my eight hours, I would work another five hours at least cleaning cars, doing what I could to make money to be able to supply.

00:16:41.600 --> 00:16:43.332
And so God started increasing me and showing me, 'Hey, this is how you do business,' and having a business mindset as a Christian.

00:16:43.332 --> 00:16:48.763
Now, there's a lot of people in the comment section that don't believe that.

00:16:48.763 --> 00:16:51.839
Why do I need to be blessed?

00:16:51.839 --> 00:16:53.820
Because you're being selfish, bottom line.

00:16:53.820 --> 00:17:04.580
If you don't want to be blessed, you're being selfish, because the kingdom of God needs you, and you need to help them.

00:17:14.422 --> 00:17:14.699
This is how the church works.

00:17:14.699 --> 00:17:29.614
I worked for churches for years, and if the people didn't give, they were talking about how they couldn't pay the mortgage, they couldn't pay the electric bill, couldn't pay the water bill.

00:17:29.614 --> 00:17:34.000
You know, there's a lot of expense to a church.

00:17:34.000 --> 00:17:43.440
There's a lot to the expenses of a ministry, and people need to get it out of their head that it just happens.

00:17:43.440 --> 00:17:44.747
No, it doesn't just happen.

00:17:49.867 --> 00:17:50.033
It comes by people giving to the ministry.

00:17:50.033 --> 00:17:53.639
So, 'Well, I just need to just take care of me.

00:17:53.639 --> 00:17:54.959
' Well, that's selfish.

00:17:54.959 --> 00:18:00.320
No, you need to believe God for more so you can help your neighbor.

00:18:00.320 --> 00:18:01.860
There is a storm coming.

00:18:01.860 --> 00:18:11.023
I'm going to tell you all, you all don't have a clue of how bad it's going to be.

00:18:11.023 --> 00:18:11.640
You don't.

00:18:11.640 --> 00:18:21.600
And I don't want to tell you in fear, but to tell you how bad—my dad and all of us have seen what's coming.

00:18:21.600 --> 00:18:26.991
It's bad, and I'm telling you the warnings from the Holy Ghost.

00:18:26.991 --> 00:18:38.847
If you jump in the river and you start falling, you're going to hear some things, and it's not about fear; it's about warning.

00:18:38.847 --> 00:18:44.280
Joseph was warned and he told Pharaoh, 'You need to store up seven years of food.

00:18:44.280 --> 00:18:51.299
You need to get ready for what's coming because there are seven years of plenty and seven years of famine.

00:18:51.299 --> 00:18:55.002
' I'm telling you all, there's a shaking coming to this nation.

00:18:55.002 --> 00:19:05.126
We have been spoiled, and you know, when a lot of people say, 'Well, that's not going to happen to us,' listen, it happened not even a hundred years ago.

00:19:05.126 --> 00:19:11.808
My granny tells me all kinds of stories; she was 106 years old.

00:19:12.216 --> 00:19:15.203
She talked about just saving foil.

00:19:16.774 --> 00:19:17.802
She wouldn't even throw foil away.

00:19:20.066 --> 00:19:24.173
She was so scared to throw foil away, thinking that there was another depression coming in her lifetime.

00:19:25.339 --> 00:19:25.806
She didn't even trust banks.

00:19:29.362 --> 00:19:30.419
She was scared spitless to even put her money in the bank.

00:19:31.477 --> 00:19:34.493
She would hide it all over the place.

00:19:34.493 --> 00:19:47.206
Before she went home to the Lord, she'd dig a hole in the yard, put it in a little canister, and shove it down in the yard, bury it.

00:19:50.880 --> 00:19:51.292
You didn't even know.

00:19:51.292 --> 00:20:07.264
I mean, that's the kind of stuff they lived through, and that was a terrible time in the 1930s, I believe is when it was.

00:20:08.314 --> 00:20:11.186
That wasn't that long ago.

00:20:11.186 --> 00:20:23.500
But we have such an entitlement right now as a culture because we've had everything—we've had air conditioning, we've had all the stuff.

00:20:25.680 --> 00:20:27.840
They didn't have it, granny, they didn't have anything.

00:20:27.840 --> 00:20:30.051
They were dead broke.

00:20:43.860 --> 00:20:44.040
They had to use the flour sacks from the flour to make clothes out of it so that they would have clothes to wear to go to school.

00:20:44.040 --> 00:20:45.913
Granny didn't have anything.

00:20:52.515 --> 00:20:52.770
They lived off of beans and rice and possum out of the yard—nasty stuff.

00:20:52.770 --> 00:21:07.620
Even before she went home to be with the Lord, she would go outside and be digging in a ditch and pull up some weeds and cut the roots off and go in and boil it and eat it.

00:21:07.620 --> 00:21:13.877
But she lived to 106 years old; she could live off anything.

00:21:13.877 --> 00:21:18.750
She'd go, 'Those are poke greens; those are dandelion greens.

00:21:18.750 --> 00:21:30.480
' She would go out there and just start digging in the yard because they lived off of that for years.

00:21:30.480 --> 00:21:31.760
That's how they lived.

00:21:31.760 --> 00:21:37.460
They starved almost a lot of times, and the farmers would all go together.

00:21:37.460 --> 00:21:55.233
She would tell me about it; they would get the eggs from the farmers and they would trade, they would barter, and they did all kinds of stuff just to survive.

00:21:55.233 --> 00:22:10.740
Even to take a bath, before she went home, she wouldn't even turn on the shower; she would just sponge bath herself every single day when she would be outside working.

00:22:10.740 --> 00:22:17.504
She had a sponge bath, and then one time a week she took a bath.

00:22:17.504 --> 00:22:19.260
That's what she did.

00:22:19.260 --> 00:22:25.800
And that was just up until a couple of years ago when she went home.

00:22:25.800 --> 00:22:31.080
That's the way she lived; it affected her that much.

00:22:45.150 --> 00:22:45.405
And so I'm trying to tell you all something.

00:22:49.760 --> 00:22:55.327
I don't know how many of you all have had relatives that had hard times and lived in hard times and saw that during the Depression.

00:22:55.327 --> 00:22:59.194
I pray we never see this stuff, I really do.

00:22:59.194 --> 00:23:01.680
I intercede all the time.

00:23:01.680 --> 00:23:13.148
But I'm telling you, I've seen pictures and the Lord will give me warnings about the wars and about people living in poverty and things happening.

00:23:14.370 --> 00:23:32.280
And God wants to raise up multi-millionaires for these last days so that we will preach the gospel and have money to help support these preachers, help tent revivals, churches, and things like that, so that they won't all go under.

00:23:32.280 --> 00:23:45.880
There are some churches, like the last church I worked for, where they borrowed seven million dollars for the mortgage on the building.

00:24:01.619 --> 00:24:01.920
A monthly payment on seven percent interest over 30 years—that's a big note.

00:24:01.920 --> 00:24:04.718
Seriously, that comes every month.

00:24:04.718 --> 00:24:18.825
There's a lot of churches in America; you've got to think of all these megachurches around here in these big towns that have all these fancy buildings that are not paid for.

00:24:27.257 --> 00:24:27.729
I believe a lot of them will probably close their doors because they won't be able to afford them.

00:24:27.729 --> 00:24:34.620
There will be a lot of home churches, Bible studies, and smaller gatherings.

00:24:34.620 --> 00:24:45.428
I've seen these smaller gatherings, and whenever major events take place, there will be big gatherings with big tents, tent revivals, and healing revivals.

00:24:45.428 --> 00:24:49.633
It's going to happen like the old 1950s tent revivals with A.

00:24:51.403 --> 00:24:51.754
A.

00:24:51.754 --> 00:24:56.649
Allen, Jack Coe, Oral Roberts, Kathryn Kuhlman, and all of them.

00:24:56.649 --> 00:25:00.802
It's going to be major tent revivals again.

00:25:00.802 --> 00:25:01.327
R.

00:25:01.327 --> 00:25:01.852
W.

00:25:01.852 --> 00:25:04.319
Schambach, we're going to see this again.

00:25:04.319 --> 00:25:18.299
I hope you all understand that I never want to preach fear, but you have to understand that you must sow a seed to reap a harvest.

00:25:28.285 --> 00:25:28.654
Every seed produces after its own kind; finances happen the same way.

00:25:35.918 --> 00:25:39.433
You might say you don't give to get, but a farmer plants a seed of corn in the field to reap corn.

00:25:39.433 --> 00:25:42.578
He plants peas in the field to reap peas.

00:25:52.219 --> 00:25:52.486
You sow in the kingdom of God to reap so you can take care of yourself too.

00:25:52.486 --> 00:26:02.910
I give so that I can sow to get what God has promised me in His word: 'good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over will men give unto you.

00:26:02.910 --> 00:26:10.613
' God will give you ideas to get wealth so that you don't have to struggle.

00:26:10.613 --> 00:26:17.130
Maybe you're good at making pies; start selling them at a bakery or something there or online.

00:26:17.130 --> 00:26:24.766
Whatever you put your hands to will prosper; He told us this in Deuteronomy 28.

00:26:24.766 --> 00:26:32.065
Read that over and over again about the blessings—everything you put your hands to will prosper.

00:26:32.768 --> 00:26:36.680
I meditate on it and get it down inside of me.

00:26:43.122 --> 00:26:54.968
The more you meditate on the word, the more it will become alive inside your spirit: you are the head and not the tail, you're above and not beneath, and you'll go through and not go under.

00:27:06.824 --> 00:27:07.087
You just have to get that word inside you; everything you put your hands to will prosper.

00:27:07.087 --> 00:27:10.480
Quote those scriptures and believe them for what's coming.

00:27:11.562 --> 00:27:13.002
I'm telling you all, a storm is coming.

00:27:13.002 --> 00:27:19.166
A lot of you don't want to hear that, thinking the Rapture of the church is coming before that happens, but no, you're wrong.

00:27:19.166 --> 00:27:21.720
Perilous times are coming.

00:27:21.720 --> 00:27:31.740
I hope you understand that before the birthing pains—it says as labor pains come upon a woman, so will it be.

00:27:43.560 --> 00:27:43.980
Jesus warned us about the birthing pains.

00:27:43.980 --> 00:27:52.570
They start out small and get more and more until the birth of the baby.

00:27:52.570 --> 00:28:02.768
Every woman who has a child knows this; it does not slack off, it increases until it's unbearable.

00:28:02.768 --> 00:28:10.680
That's the way it's going to be: more frequent until the birthing of us leaving in the Rapture of the church.

00:28:10.680 --> 00:28:18.327
Some of you don't believe in the Rapture; that's fine, I do, but we are going to see some things.

00:28:26.100 --> 00:28:26.383
The weather's going to start getting even crazier: the heatwaves, the rain, and the droughts.

00:28:29.080 --> 00:28:35.653
I really believe with all my heart we're going to see it.

00:28:48.413 --> 00:28:48.600
That's why the Lord has talked to me about having a well, water shortages, a generator for power, and food storage.

00:28:48.600 --> 00:28:51.648
He talked to me about securing your home better.

00:28:51.648 --> 00:28:57.269
Just three years ago, people were going crazy in San Francisco, robbing and looting whenever COVID was going on.

00:28:57.269 --> 00:29:05.987
People were fighting over toilet paper; you would almost lose your life over a roll of toilet paper.

00:29:20.610 --> 00:29:20.940
If there's no food on the shelf—and I warned you there were cobwebs in some supermarkets—it's even worse in major populated areas.

00:29:20.940 --> 00:29:34.107
If they're willing to hurt you for a roll of toilet paper, how much more are they going to hurt you for a gallon of milk, bread, canned food, or meat?

00:29:34.107 --> 00:29:36.960
Spam is going to become a big deal.

00:29:48.454 --> 00:29:48.737
People get crazy when they can't get food.

00:29:48.737 --> 00:29:57.817
I'm just trying to help you; I can only lead you to the water, but I can't force you to drink.

00:29:57.817 --> 00:30:00.473
I'm believing God for the Iraqi dinar.

00:30:00.747 --> 00:30:03.188
The Lord showed me Babylon rising again.

00:30:03.188 --> 00:30:10.132
Babylon was the breadbasket of the world at one time, and I believe it will be again.

00:30:10.830 --> 00:30:13.410
I believe there's a shifting coming in Iraq.

00:30:23.970 --> 00:30:24.225
I believe the people who are listening to the Spirit of God about crypto and these things are not going to struggle.

00:30:24.225 --> 00:30:34.173
God's going to give creative ideas to provide for the people who are listening to Him and praying in the Spirit.

00:30:35.533 --> 00:30:38.069
You need to read your Bible and pray in tongues.

00:30:38.069 --> 00:30:44.767
The Lord wants everybody to have that prayer language so you don't have to let the devil hear you.

00:30:44.767 --> 00:30:55.868
Walking in the Holy Ghost is what you're going to have to do in these last days—knowing the name of Jesus and understanding the power in the blood.

00:30:55.868 --> 00:31:01.207
Just like the greats like Smith Wigglesworth, walking in the authority of the believer.

00:31:02.794 --> 00:31:07.422
I hope I didn't freak you out; I'm just trying to be real with you today.

00:31:07.422 --> 00:31:14.160
It's not really a sermon; it's just me being real and telling you where I'm at.

00:31:14.160 --> 00:31:19.880
I don't live in fear, but I live with my ear towards Him.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Regarding the financial outpouring, not everybody's going to participate; some people will stay broke, just like it was in the.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
com era.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Jesus told us the poor will be with you always.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.250
I don't want to be one of them; I want to be the man with the pitcher in his hand helping folks, being able to say I can help you with some rice or beans.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
But it takes money to get a surplus; groceries are expensive right now.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
To go to Sam's or Costco and buy in bulk takes thousands of dollars.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
God takes care of the widow, the orphan, and the sparrow; how much more does He care about you?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
Start studying people like George Mueller and how he took care of the orphans.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
I watched it on VeggieTales, but then I studied and realized this man really existed and lived by faith.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
You're going to have to learn to live by faith.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
I hope this talk blessed you today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Thank you for watching, the subscribes, the likes, and the Facebook shares.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Do not share my videos on YouTube.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
I mean that when I'm telling you to share my video, do not share my videos on YouTube.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
You're not copying my material and putting it on your page; this is my stuff.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Preach your own sermon and put your own thing out there.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Don't put my stuff out there on your YouTube channel or whatever.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
You can share it on your Facebook; that's what I mean when I'm saying to share it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Share it on Facebook, Instagram, or Twitter.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
All right, well we thank you so much for your support.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
We love you so much and we'll see you next time.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
